column5: How has it been this year?
I hear they are biting as usual. Many big fish.
Hi Jeff,Think I responded with you last year about Gullrock. Will be up there next week. Any new hotspots that you've heard?

I heard about Gullrock Bay, Stone Bay, and all around boot island. this is shallower water. That report was from last week. I talked with the camp on Thursday, said fishing was extremely good. You should have no problems. Please let us know about your week.ThanksJeff
